                                "Under the version of \u00a7 1026.35(c)(2)(viii) that goes into effect on July 18, 2015, loans secured by an existing manufactured home and land together will be subject to the HMPL appraisal requirements in \u00a7 1026.35(c)(3) through (6), consistent with the January 2013 Final Rule and the 2013 Supplemental Proposed Rule."
